          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Content Elements",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Consider and choose content elements carefully. Test your cards with the minimal content and only add additional content where they give needed context to the user. Content types in cards include:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "Headline",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " - Provides snapshot of the content.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "Copy",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " - Provides further details where the headline alone may not be sufficient.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "Label",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " - Indicates the category of a topic or theme when a user needs to further group content. For example, departments, agencies or services.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "Date",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " - Indicates how old the content is when this information is important to the user.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        },
        {
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Images",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Using an image allows for different content to stand out and provide additional context. It helps users visualise different pieces of information and quickly distinguish between content to find information easily.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Test your visual elements carefully:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "only use images where it supports and re-enforces the content to the user",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "only use images when they can clearly show the difference between content and can be easily identified",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "do not use for decorative purposes only",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        }
      ],
      "type": "doc"
    }
  },
